

The rMP3 library requires an updated NewSoftSerial Library
Source: http://www.roguerobotics.com/wikidocs/code/library/arduino/roguemp3#rogue_robotics_mp3_playback_module_interface_library_usage

Ardino Serail Base Class:
http://www.roguerobotics.com/wikidocs/code/arduino_serial_base_class

    1. Download the Arduino with Stream Core.
        http://rogue-code.googlecode.com/files/ArduinoCore-Stream.zip
        
    2. Install into SKETCHBOOK/hardware folder (create the hardware folder if it doesn't exist).
    
    3. Start the IDE and select one of the ”(Stream)” version of your board from the Tools|Board menu.
    
    4. NewSoftSerial and other libraries with Stream modifications can be downloaded from:
        

